    What to take
  </h3>

  <p>
    This will be a very hot day. But since we will be on a boat, it can get windy and a little colder. I recommend you to bring 2 outfits: 1. For the house and other moments, bathing suit/bikini + a t-shirt/dress. 2. For the boat and for later hours(a jacket
    + tracksuit pants). PLEASE ALSO BRING SUNSCREEN and cash, the drinks at the house are not included. Besides that the normal beachwear: a towel, hat, sunglasses and all the toys you feel are welcome to party with us.
  </p>
</div>


