  <h3>
    Respect
  </h3>

  <p>
    Remember this is a party from friends to friends. You might not know the person next to you, but be sure they know somebody you do. So please be kind, avoid conflicts, invite everyone to participate in your jokes and allow people to not want to join.
    Drink with responsibility, this will be a full day of partying so take time to rest during the day so you can enjoy the whole event.
